methods.name: getJobOverviewFromName
methods.body: /**↵@param filter optional hash. See @ref archfiltering for more info.↵@return the approximate number of workflow order data instances that would be purged. Hash keys are:↵ - c live: order count in COMPLETE or CANCELED status older than 'days-interval'↵ - c prepared: count if rows in tge internal helper table ARCH_WF_INSTANCES↵*/↵hash sub estimated_counts(*hash filter) {↵    return new Archiving(MODE_MAINTENANCE, 0, filter).estimatedCounts();↵}↵
methods.description: gets job overview, params: [date, [name]]: If no date is given, default = last 24 hours
